###
### Mus API tests
### Ejecutable con la extension REST Client de Visual Studio Code
###

@host = localhost
@port = 8080
@baseUrl = http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/mus

### Cambia este valor por el gameId devuelto por "Crear partida"
@gameId = 11


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 1. Crear partida
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "players": [
    {"id": "P1", "name": "Luis", "type": "human", "team": "A"},
    {"id": "P2", "name": "Bot 1", "type": "agent", "team": "B"},
    {"id": "P3", "name": "Partner", "type": "agent", "team": "A"},
    {"id": "P4", "name": "Bot 2", "type": "agent", "team": "B"}
  ]
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. Iniciar partida
### Esperado: phase = descartes, discardsApplied = false
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/start
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. Consultar estado inicial
### Usa esta respuesta para ver las cartas si quieres probar descartes con cartas reales.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 4. Intentar jugar antes de descartar
### Esperado: error DISCARDS_REQUIRED
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 5. Aplicar descartes de todos los jugadores, sin descartar cartas
### Esperado: phase pasa de descartes a grande, turnPlayerId = P1
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": ["4B"],
    "P4": ["4C"]
  }
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 6. Consultar estado tras descartes
### Esperado: phase = grande, turnPlayerId = P1
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 7. P1 envida en grande
### Esperado: pendingBet para el equipo A, respondingTeam = B, siguiente turno P2
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 8. P2 quiere el envite
### Esperado: se resuelve grande, se suman puntos y phase pasa a chica
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 9. Consultar marcador tras resolver grande
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Flujo alternativo: descartes con cartas reales
### Sustituye las cartas por las que devuelva GET /state justo despues de start.
### Ejecutalo en una partida nueva, antes del bloque de envido.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": ["1O"],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": ["10C"],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Flujo alternativo: P2 no quiere el envite
### Ejecutalo en una partida nueva despues de descartes y despues de que P1 envida.
### Esperado: equipo A suma 1 punto y phase pasa a chica.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "no_querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Caso negativo: faltan descartes de P4
### Esperado: MISSING_PLAYER_DISCARDS
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": []
  }
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Caso negativo: descartar una carta que no pertenece al jugador
### Esperado: INVALID_DISCARDS
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": ["99X"],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Caso negativo: volver a descartar en la misma mano
### Esperado: INVALID_PHASE o DISCARDS_ALREADY_APPLIED
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Caso negativo: querer sin apuesta pendiente
### Ejecutar despues de descartes, antes de envidar.
### Esperado: NO_PENDING_BET
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Caso negativo: jugador fuera de turno
### Esperado: NOT_PLAYER_TURN
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}